title: com.readyeducation.uog

creator: University of Guelph
descriptionHtml:
The IAmAGryphon App brings campus to your fingertips and enables you to connect with the Univeristy of Guelph community: Stay on top of your events, classes, and assignments with the built in calendar function, and get notified of important dates, deadlines & security announcements. Make friends, ask questions, and access campus resources at any time!

Some other exciting features include:
+ EVENTS: Discover campus events, set reminders, and track your attendance
+ FEATURED ACTIVITIES: Orientation, Homecoming, etc.
+ CAMPUS COMMUNITY: Meet friends, ask questions, and keep up with what's happening on the campus wall.
+ GROUPS & CLUBS: Get involved with campus organizations and meet people with similar interests
+ CAMPUS SERVICES: Learn about services offered, such as Academic Advising, Financial Aid & Counselling.
+ PUSH NOTIFICATIONS: Receive important campus notifications and emergency alerts.
+ CAMPUS MAP: Find the quickest route to classes, events, and offices.

The IAmAGryphon App brings campus to your fingertips and enables you to connect with the Univeristy of Guelph community: Stay on top of your events, classes, and assignments with the built in calendar function, and get notified of important dates, deadlines & security announcements. Make friends, ask questions, and access campus resources at any time!
Some other exciting features include:
+ EVENTS: Discover campus events, set reminders, and track your attendance
+ FEATURED ACTIVITIES: Orientation, Homecoming, etc.
+ CAMPUS COMMUNITY: Meet friends, ask questions, and keep up with what's happening on the campus wall.
+ GROUPS & CLUBS: Get involved with campus organizations and meet people with similar interests
+ CAMPUS SERVICES: Learn about services offered, such as Academic Advising, Financial Aid & Counselling.
+ PUSH NOTIFICATIONS: Receive important campus notifications and emergency alerts.
+ CAMPUS MAP: Find the quickest route to classes, events, and offices.
descriptionShort: The official app for the IAmAGryphon University of Guelph student experience

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We improve the app for our users with bi-weekly updates to add new features, squash bugs and improve app performance. We'd love to hear from you if you have any feedback for us.
